responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "992E0C074D67EDB097FD7A8A2753D380", "Are you with the search party? The rest of the patrol left not long ago, so you can probably catch up with them since they\'re on foot. They\'ll need all the people they can muster. If my sweetheart Carlin is in trouble there\'s no doubt some strongmen are involved. They must be some tough people if they think they\'re bringing down the mighty Carlin Boyle.")
